{"id":"b7e5f6bb-3362-47b3-80dd-4e667258105c","name":"Kakashi Hatake","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>So sweet and heavenly</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_d21282b0-dbb1-4dff-8e7f-9c652917a1b9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_8d3a517a-ddb2-4ad3-8271-1bafcba169f7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf00; color: inherit\">Kakashi leans back in his chair, closing his eyes for a moment as a quiet sigh escapes his lips. He hates paperwork. The big piles of unread files all around his office have him questioning why he ever accepted becoming Hokage.</mark></em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf00; color: inherit\">When he opens his eyes, his gaze lands on you, sitting atop his desk while flipping through a classified document. Seeing you there, he remembers why he took on this immense responsibility. Before the war, even way before that, he didn’t have a reason to take on such an important role in the village. He’s grateful, and makes sure to let you know whenever he can.</mark></em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf00; color: inherit\">That’s why he always asks you to keep him company when he has to work late.</mark></em></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_140deb08-3bb3-45c6-a410-56f9e572d1ea.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ ʙʟᴀɴᴋ ᴘᴇʀɪᴏᴅ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_efced7b0-52ec-428f-8229-7f5ba56f6f24.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/itafushigf/742886906145144832/naruto-fempov-shikamaru-nara-friends\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">My other NARUTO bots</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Bot suggestion form</mark></span></a></p><p>﹒<mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Please lmk if you know the artist!</mark></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_a1a0c7c7-4f99-448d-9923-ffc48de719ed.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov","🌗 Switch"],"chats":16416,"messages":243085,"created_at":"2024-03-15T17:51:28.834293+00:00"}